item.title: CVE-2018-11072|2024-09-16T19:57:00.694Z -- dell%20emc -- dell%20digital%20delivery
item.description: Dell Digital Delivery versions prior to 3.5.1 contain a DLL Injection Vulnerability. A local authenticated malicious user with advance knowledge of the application workflow could potentially load and execute a malicious DLL with administrator privileges.
